Altogether, these additive effects lead to an estimated increase of 20 (benzene rings) + 20 (benzene rings) + 30 (nitro group) + 15 (nitrile group) + 25 (hydrazone linkage) + 25 (conjugated system) above the base value of the melting point of benzene.
